---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="New Construction Plumbing"
  description={`New construction plumbing services in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC for residential and commercial projects. Call ${site.phone} to learn more.`}
  heroTitle="New Construction Plumbing"
  heroSubtitle="Provide your property with impervious plumbing: new construction plumbing services in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-18.jpg"
  listHeading="3 reasons it's important to have reliable plumbing"
  listItems={[
    'Establish a strong system that will stand the test of time',
    'Prevent malfunctions by completing thorough work the first time',
    'Install quality and efficient components and appliances',
  ]}
  listNote="Consult Nesbitt's Plumbing today about establishing the plumbing in your new construction project."
  ctaHeading="Building Something New?"
>
  <p>
    You're working on a construction project in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC, and you want to
    make sure that every part of it comes together perfectly. If you're in need of an expert to
    establish the plumbing in your project, turn to Nesbitt's Plumbing. We have the equipment to
    complete site work in commercial and residential projects.
  </p>
  <p>
    Dial <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    to learn more about our new construction services.
  </p>
  <p>
    You want to make sure the plumbing in your property is dependable from the very beginning.
    Our crews install strong, efficient systems that stand the test of time.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
